1
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:26,300
♪The gentle breeze leaves no trace♪

2
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:29,670
♪It stirs the old times♪

3
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:33,560
♪Love is gained and lost♪

4
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:37,370
♪Only then does it become unforgettable♪

5
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:41,370
♪The bamboo leaves
are rustling and falling♪

6
00:00:41,370 --> 00:00:44,770
♪Fate is delayed and scattered♪

7
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:48,840
♪Only lingering hatred remains♪

8
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:51,210
♪Echoing♪

9
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,130
♪Old dreams are like illusions♪

10
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:59,490
♪Alas, the world is too indifferent♪

11
00:00:59,490 --> 00:01:01,760
♪If there were no obsession♪

12
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:05,870
♪I wouldn't be thinking of someone♪

13
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:09,630
♪If it's destined to be alone♪

14
00:01:09,630 --> 00:01:13,310
♪Like a snowstorm♪

15
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:15,980
♪When love and hate dissolve♪

16
00:01:15,980 --> 00:01:20,940
♪Only a long gaze remains♪

17
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:25,610
♪A drop of tear♪

18
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:29,490
♪Falls, burning my heart♪

19
00:01:29,490 --> 00:01:33,340
♪We loved without regret♪

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,580
=My Destined Consort=

21
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:39,620
=Episode 22=

22
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:41,240
You scoundrel!

23
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:43,190
You've disgraced me completely!

24
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:45,110
Tell the Prefect everything

25
00:01:45,110 --> 00:01:47,240
you did now!

26
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,560
Tell us the truth.

27
00:01:50,790 --> 00:01:51,670
It was her.

28
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,270
She knew my mother was seriously ill.

29
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,470
She even gave me money

30
00:01:54,470 --> 00:01:55,600
to help her with something.

31
00:01:55,990 --> 00:01:57,750
But I never thought

32
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:00,080
I'd end up doing such a thing.

33
00:02:02,990 --> 00:02:04,080
I don't know anything.

34
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,350
He's slandering me.

35
00:02:07,270 --> 00:02:08,950
Don't think a helper's word

36
00:02:08,950 --> 00:02:10,720
is enough to clear this up.

37
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,880
Everything Qingniang said

38
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,470
matches Yanyan's features.

39
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,000
Besides,

40
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,910
what about the wound on his wrist?

41
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:22,750
These days,

42
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:23,910
I've also been thinking.

43
00:02:24,410 --> 00:02:26,060
Kids around Yanyan's age

44
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:28,040
tend to look quite similar.

45
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,840
As for the scar,

46
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,470
Qingniang said

47
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:32,910
her child was burned

48
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,750
when he was little.

49
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,160
But Yanyan was burned

50
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,630
just a short while ago.

51
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,350
If we bring in our physician,

52
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,790
he should be able to tell

53
00:02:39,790 --> 00:02:41,070
if the scar is new or old.

54
00:02:44,510 --> 00:02:45,550
As for that spirit tablet,

55
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:46,880
it seems

56
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,470
someone aged it on purpose

57
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,510
and put it in Rain Chamber.

58
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:52,510
Qingniang, do you know this maid?

59
00:02:56,350 --> 00:02:57,190
Yes...

60
00:03:00,950 --> 00:03:01,910
No...

61
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:04,320
I don't remember.

62
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:05,350
You liar!

63
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,840
Spouting nonsense and lies!

64
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,000
Mother.

65
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,160
Qingniang didn't lie.

66
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,790
The men I sent to Pei Village

67
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:15,930
have returned with a report.

68
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,950
Qingniang did have a four-year-old son.

69
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,350
And the details they gathered

70
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:21,720
match everything

71
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,600
Qingniang said.

72
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,750
It's complicated,

73
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,160
so I've invited Mr. Chu of Wind Pavilion

74
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,190
to explain it to you.

75
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,400
Very well. Summon Mr. Chu.

76
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,000
Our investigation

77
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,950
confirms that Qingniang
once had a child,

78
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,910
but her Xuan

79
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:50,190
only exists in her mind.

80
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,340
Years ago, while traveling the world,

81
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,230
I passed your ancestral tomb

82
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,810
and saved Jiangli
who was pregnant at the time.

83
00:03:56,950 --> 00:03:58,630
Yanyan's parentage is clear.

84
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,630
Now, someone is trying

85
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,720
to twist the truth.

86
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,470
I can't let that go.

87
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:05,790
Zimo,

88
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,510
do you mean

89
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,560
Qingniang is suffering from hysteria?

90
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,160
During our earlier conversation,

91
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,600
Qingniang said Xuan went missing

92
00:04:15,950 --> 00:04:17,670
six months ago at a pavilion
by Ping Lake.

93
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,110
But that pavilion was torn down

94
00:04:20,110 --> 00:04:20,950
over a year ago.

95
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,560
So, I believe

96
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,960
Xuan has passed away.

97
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:27,040
After a severe emotional blow,

98
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,200
some people will block out
painful memories.

99
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,270
That's why

100
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:34,570
Qingniang fabricated a story
of her son going missing

101
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,310
because she couldn't face
the truth of his death.

102
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,440
Sir.

103
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,480
Sir?

104
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:46,470
Did someone in your family pass away?

105
00:04:47,690 --> 00:04:48,990
I want to ask you about someone.

106
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,470
It's Qingniang.

107
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,430
Who?

108
00:04:53,670 --> 00:04:55,110
It's Qingniang.

109
00:04:55,910 --> 00:04:57,160
Qingniang?

110
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,000
Sorry, goodbye.

111
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:00,720
Oh, you mean

112
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:03,790
the one whose child died?

113
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,470
Xuan, be good.

114
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:10,720
I will take you home.

115
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,840
Be good. Don't be scared, Xuan.

116
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:16,110
I will take you home.

117
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,600
Father.

118
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:21,760
Losing a child

119
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,980
is already unbearable.

120
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,640
But someone even

121
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,640
exploited that pain.

122
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,310
It's despicable.

123
00:05:27,550 --> 00:05:28,900
- Father, please
- We'll go home.

124
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,720
give justice to Jiangli and Qingniang.

125
00:05:31,470 --> 00:05:32,760
How dare you

126
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,080
harm my eldest grandson?

127
00:05:35,350 --> 00:05:36,840
Confess now!

128
00:05:38,110 --> 00:05:39,800
It was her! She made me do it!

129
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,650
I...

130
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:41,670
And the spirit tablet.

131
00:05:42,230 --> 00:05:43,070
Did you

132
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:44,190
bribe the servants

133
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,920
to place it in Rain Chamber?

134
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,390
I plead guilty.

135
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,160
I did it all by myself.

136
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:56,840
Xuan...

137
00:05:57,350 --> 00:05:58,190
Ma'am,

138
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,760
have you seen my Xuan?

139
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,400
This is a deserted place.

140
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,480
Whose child would be here?

141
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,910
Ma'am, please think again.

142
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,200
My Xuan had a round face.

143
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,990
He looked so blessed.

144
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:09,960
We haven't seen him.

145
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,640
Xuan...

146
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:15,840
Xuan...

147
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:18,280
She's lost her child. What a poor woman.

148
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,790
I lost my mother, and she lost her son.

149
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:23,120
- We're both pitiful.
- Xuan...

150
00:06:23,530 --> 00:06:24,840
Let's visit her often.

151
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,040
Give her some money.

152
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:29,190
Ma'am.

153
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,880
Ma'am.

154
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,470
Please take this money.

155
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,600
My Lady,

156
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:40,800
I'm sorry.

157
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,040
I lied to you.

158
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:48,950
My Lord,

159
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:51,040
ever since Consort Qilan miscarried,

160
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,870
she's been drowning in tears every day.

161
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:54,470
But then,

162
00:06:54,910 --> 00:06:56,430
Consort Jiangli brought her son back

163
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,580
and won all the favor.

164
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,080
I couldn't bear to see

165
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,230
Consort Qilan

166
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,280
being treated so coldly

167
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:04,520
so I resort to this.

168
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,870
When I returned home to visit my family,

169
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,110
I ran into Qingniang,
who was acting strangely.

170
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:11,670
So, I lured her to Dongzhou

171
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:13,040
to search for her child.

172
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,720
I also bribed the helper to change

173
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:17,600
Young Master Yanyan's attire.

174
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,110
Then I secretly made

175
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:21,400
a fake spirit tablet.

176
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:24,090
While Master Jingming
and Consort Jiangli were away,

177
00:07:24,090 --> 00:07:25,180
I bribed the servants

178
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,430
to place it in Rain Chamber.

179
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,520
I don't believe you did this yourself.

180
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,070
You must be taking the blame
for your lady.

181
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,550
No, no.

182
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:34,520
This was all my idea.

183
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,540
I didn't...

184
00:07:35,550 --> 00:07:37,200
Ms. Qilan had no idea about this.

185
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,440
My Lord.

186
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,720
My Lord, please believe me.

187
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,040
Take them both out of here

188
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,460
and cane them to death.

189
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,560
My Lord.

190
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:45,950
Fuling...

191
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:49,800
- My Lady.
- Master Jingxiu.

192
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,000
Fuling...

193
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:52,190
Fuling...

194
00:07:52,990 --> 00:07:54,450
Is this how you discipline your maid?

195
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,520
I'm sorry.

196
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,160
Father, Mother,

197
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,430
since Qilan married me,

198
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:09,010
she's always been careful and cautious.

199
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:11,390
It must've been after losing her son
and her mother

200
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,260
that she became lax
in managing the servants.

201
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:14,870
Father, Mother, please

202
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,760
let Qilan stay in the mansion

203
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,800
and reflect on her mistakes

204
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:18,870
in seclusion.

205
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,230
You'd better repent this time.

206
00:08:21,690 --> 00:08:23,510
If it weren't for the upcoming
Peace Banquet,

207
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,230
I wouldn't let this slide.

208
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:26,070
Yes.

209
00:08:26,230 --> 00:08:27,790
Enough. You may all leave now.

210
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,440
Thank you, Father.

211
00:08:33,910 --> 00:08:34,880
Qilan, get up.

212
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,430
Jiangli,

213
00:09:06,430 --> 00:09:07,830
you are skilled in medicine.

214
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,240
Please check

215
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,640
Qingniang's condition.

216
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:12,270
Yes.

217
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,510
My Lord.

218
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:16,520
Let's go see our grandson.

219
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,120
- Sure.
- Let's go.

220
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,720
Ma'am.

221
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,030
Here.

222
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:32,630
Jiangli,

223
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,010
are you really going to wake her up?

224
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:36,670
After waking her,

225
00:09:37,590 --> 00:09:39,000
she might be even more painful.

226
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,590
I'm just temporarily

227
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:41,790
stabilizing her mind.

228
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,910
Whether she can overcome it

229
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,160
depends on her own will.

230
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,380
Let's go home.

231
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,640
Xuan.

232
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,520
Xuan...

233
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:58,950
Xuan.

234
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,190
Xuan, my Xuan...

235
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:07,590
Xuan...

236
00:10:07,590 --> 00:10:08,430
Xuan.

237
00:10:08,590 --> 00:10:09,790
My Xuan.

238
00:10:11,070 --> 00:10:12,790
My Xuan...

239
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,890
Xuan...

240
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:20,240
This is Qingniang's home.

241
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:23,670
Thank you, sir.

242
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:29,910
Xuan,

243
00:10:30,190 --> 00:10:32,190
look at the toys I bought you.

244
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:35,190
Xuan, Xuan...

245
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:43,120
At the beginning of life,

246
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,240
people are inherently good.

247
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:46,880
Xuan...

248
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,830
My Xuan...

249
00:10:54,830 --> 00:10:57,360
I'll make a belt for Xuan.

250
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:00,670
I met her when her child

251
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,760
had been dead for several days.

252
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:07,280
I offered to help her bury him,

253
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:08,750
but she...

254
00:11:08,980 --> 00:11:09,830
Xuan...

255
00:11:09,830 --> 00:11:11,950
- She refused to let it go.
- I'm here.

256
00:11:11,950 --> 00:11:13,160
Xuan, don't be afraid.

257
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:16,880
Xuan...

258
00:11:23,780 --> 00:11:25,380
(Ride with Wind)

259
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,160
So many candied hawthorns.

260
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:28,190
Here.

261
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:29,830
Let me choose the biggest one

262
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,520
for you, okay?

263
00:11:33,310 --> 00:11:34,190
Yanyan.

264
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:35,240
Mother!

265
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:37,710
I miss you so much.

266
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,950
I miss you too.

267
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:45,270
Let's go home.

268
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:04,030
My Lady,

269
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,160
are we really going to do this?

270
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,240
The child she described
looks just like Yanyan,

271
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:12,750
and we met her

272
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:14,590
when we saw Mother.

273
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,760
This must be Mother's will,

274
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:17,950
sending help from above.

275
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:19,390
Isn't this

276
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,830
too risky?

277
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,760
You've seen how the Prefect

278
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,880
treats Master Jingming and his family.

279
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,670
This child's appearance

280
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,170
already threatens
Master Jingxiu's position.

281
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,790
For the sake of Master Jingxiu,

282
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,550
I must take this chance.

283
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,520
But Qingniang

284
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:36,160
looks mentally unstable.

285
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,760
What if I can't control her?

286
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:39,480
I know.

287
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:42,160
That's why this is a double-edged sword.

288
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,830
But I'm betting

289
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:46,360
on the Prefect's suspicion.

290
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:52,240
If things go wrong,

291
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:55,040
