292
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:55,880
My Lady.

293
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,280
My Lady, don't worry.

294
00:12:58,790 --> 00:13:00,280
I will handle everything.

295
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:19,040
Xizhou is sending

296
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:21,400
the Grand Lady
and the Grand Princess here.

297
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,280
So, we must maintain

298
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,590
proper manners.

299
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,710
Leave the upcoming

300
00:13:26,710 --> 00:13:28,240
Peace Banquet to Jiangli.

301
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:30,430
My Lord, just leave it to Jiangli.

302
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:32,890
She will manage it perfectly.

303
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:35,600
Qinian,

304
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,550
the Peace Banquet is of high importance.

305
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,160
The Grand Princess

306
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,940
and the Grand Lady from Xizhou
will be here.

307
00:13:41,190 --> 00:13:44,000
Qilan, as Jingxiu's consort,

308
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,880
can't miss this banquet.

309
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,310
How dare you mention

310
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:48,280
that useless child to me?

311
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,910
I haven't even settled

312
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:51,360
the score with you yet.

313
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:52,670
Xiulan,

314
00:13:52,950 --> 00:13:55,160
we can deal
with our private matters later,

315
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:57,520
but we can't let disgrace our family.

316
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:59,360
You must think of the bigger picture.

317
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:00,910
Qinian,

318
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,400
please give Qilan

319
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,040
a chance to make amends.

320
00:14:05,310 --> 00:14:07,480
Lady Wang has a point.

321
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,790
Our guests are of high status,

322
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,160
and we can't let our manners slip.

323
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:12,310
Let her assist Jiangli.

324
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:13,240
Let her try her best.

325
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:15,070
She can't make any mistakes.

326
00:14:15,430 --> 00:14:16,590
If there's any mistake,

327
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:18,070
no one can protect her.

328
00:14:19,070 --> 00:14:19,950
Thank you, My Lord.

329
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:27,550
Last time,
your maid took the fall for you.

330
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:30,640
You won't always be that lucky.

331
00:14:31,070 --> 00:14:32,000
I understand.

332
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:33,830
I'll be more careful from now on.

333
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:37,240
The banquet is your chance
to turn things around.

334
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,160
I pleaded with the Prefect

335
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,310
for this opportunity.

336
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:42,190
Don't mess it up again.

337
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:44,430
I will remember this.

338
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,320
The embroidery looks good.

339
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,760
This gold embroidery

340
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,360
is unique

341
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,550
to Dongzhou.

342
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:07,400
It'll be presented
to the ladies of Xizhou

343
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,240
as a gift.

344
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,640
Tell the embroiderers

345
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:11,960
that they must do their best.

346
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,720
If these embroidered handkerchiefs
gain popularity in Xizhou,

347
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:16,550
you may even open up a business there.

348
00:15:17,060 --> 00:15:18,190
Don't worry, Consort Jiangli.

349
00:15:18,190 --> 00:15:19,710
I won't slack off.

350
00:15:19,950 --> 00:15:20,950
We won't

351
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,190
disgrace Dongzhou.

352
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,120
Sir?

353
00:15:26,590 --> 00:15:27,430
Go ahead.

354
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,710
I'll take another look around.

355
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:30,640
Yes, Consort Jiangli. Take your time.

356
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,590
Oh, it's Consort Qilan.

357
00:15:34,590 --> 00:15:35,640
Sorry about my negligence.

358
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,710
Please forgive me.

359
00:15:37,190 --> 00:15:38,030
Sir,

360
00:15:38,090 --> 00:15:40,270
I'd like to order
100 gold-embroidered handkerchiefs.

361
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:41,590
What would that cost me?

362
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:43,950
My apologies, Consort Qilan.

363
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:45,000
We can't manage that now.

364
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,910
We've just taken on a huge order.

365
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:50,360
All our embroiderers are swamped.

366
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,880
We're overwhelmed now.

367
00:15:52,710 --> 00:15:54,160
You're too late.

368
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:56,740
I've placed an order
for over 100 handkerchiefs.

369
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:01,310
So, it was you, Jiangli.

370
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:14,240
We're truly sisters.

371
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:15,190
Looks like we are

372
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,590
of one mind.

373
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:18,510
Shen Qilan,

374
00:16:19,190 --> 00:16:20,160
spare me

375
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:21,400
the sisterly act.

376
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,040
You tried to frame me

377
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:24,880
with Qingniang, right?

378
00:16:25,190 --> 00:16:26,030
Yes.

379
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,640
Did you just figure it out?

380
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:31,790
What will you do now?

381
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,080
Are you going to report me?

382
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,480
I don't even need to act

383
00:16:37,950 --> 00:16:39,430
because you'll trap yourself

384
00:16:39,430 --> 00:16:40,550
just like your mother.

385
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,390
Shen Jiangli.

386
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,760
You don't deserve to mention my mother.

387
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:47,710
The Qingniang incident

388
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,640
was merely my opening move.

389
00:16:50,070 --> 00:16:50,910
The Peace Banquet

390
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,520
is the beginning.

391
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,000
I've prepared tea for you.

392
00:16:58,670 --> 00:16:59,510
Come in.

393
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:02,240
Jiangli,
you truly have an eye for design.

394
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:03,590
This pattern

395
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:04,720
is exquisite.

396
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,340
I must learn more

397
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:08,000
from you in the future.

398
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,550
Qilan, you flatter me.

399
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,520
But you'll need to learn

400
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:14,870
more than just choosing handkerchiefs.

401
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:16,870
When the chance comes,

402
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,000
I'll teach you everything.

403
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,200
Thank you, Jiangli.

404
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:37,220
(Prefect's Mansion)

405
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:42,150
I've prepared
gold-embroidered handkerchiefs

406
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:44,070
to gift the guests from Xizhou.

407
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:45,550
Each one was made

408
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:47,870
by the finest embroiderers in Dongzhou

409
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:49,550
with auspicious phrases

410
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:52,240
and Buddhist totems on it.

411
00:17:52,870 --> 00:17:54,240
We always gift visitors

412
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,960
gold-embroidered handkerchiefs.

413
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,150
It's getting old.

414
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,920
Seems Consort Jiangli

415
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:00,720
