416
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,350
Qilan, what have you prepared?

417
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,040
Mother,

418
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:06,760
My Lord,

419
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,830
the autumn skies are clear,

420
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:11,390
and the red maples of East Mountain
are a local marvel.

421
00:18:11,870 --> 00:18:13,960
I plan to invite the ladies of Xizhou

422
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,870
to admire the maples.

423
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:18,240
I've also arranged lantern riddles
and drinking games,

424
00:18:18,390 --> 00:18:20,280
so they can paint among the maples.

425
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:22,000
They'll surely have a good time.

426
00:18:22,630 --> 00:18:24,550
Qilan must be telling a joke.

427
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,720
A group of ladies climbing a mountain?

428
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,590
What if they scratch their faces?

429
00:18:28,690 --> 00:18:29,870
Can you take responsibility?

430
00:18:30,870 --> 00:18:31,710
Besides,

431
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,200
the ladies of Xizhou

432
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,440
are no match for our refined ladies.

433
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:37,870
You want them to write poems?

434
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:40,830
You're helping with the banquet,

435
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:43,590
yet you didn't even research
their preferences?

436
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,310
Please, Father,

437
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:51,680
take a look at the programs
I've prepared

438
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,890
before making a final decision.

439
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:54,350
No need.

440
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:57,240
The Peace Banquet
should be festive and lively.

441
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,830
Just keep things lighthearted.

442
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,960
No need to have poetic events.

443
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:03,960
Jiangli's embroidered handkerchiefs

444
00:19:04,390 --> 00:19:06,070
may not be fresh,

445
00:19:06,390 --> 00:19:07,720
but they're a safe

446
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:09,200
and thoughtful gift.

447
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:11,050
With different auspicious phrases

448
00:19:11,060 --> 00:19:12,930
on each one,

449
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:15,000
you must've put much effort into this.

450
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,150
Well done.

451
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:18,140
Thank you for your praise, Father.

452
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,920
It is my duty.

453
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:23,580
Qingqing,

454
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:25,300
the new ruler of Xizhou is still young.

455
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:26,870
So, the Grand Lady and Grand Princess

456
00:19:26,870 --> 00:19:28,520
are involved in state affairs.

457
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:30,040
Those two

458
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:31,720
hold great power in Xizhou.

459
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:33,000
So,

460
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,840
their visit here

461
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,310
this time

462
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:37,720
isn't just for the Peace Banquet.

463
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,680
As the princess of Dongzhou,

464
00:19:39,870 --> 00:19:41,830
you should prepare
a welcoming performance

465
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,520
to showcase the elegance of Dongzhou

466
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:45,040
in front of the princess of Xizhou.

467
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,790
I'll prepare it carefully.

468
00:19:55,870 --> 00:19:57,040
What should I do?

469
00:19:57,830 --> 00:19:59,390
What to do?

470
00:19:59,630 --> 00:20:01,630
What should I perform?

471
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:02,840
Qingqing,

472
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,680
as the princess of Dongzhou,

473
00:20:04,810 --> 00:20:06,520
you must have attended
many grand events.

474
00:20:06,870 --> 00:20:08,390
Why are you so nervous this time?

475
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:09,630
It's different this time.

476
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:12,520
Everyone in the four states knows

477
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,870
Princess Chuya excels in everything,

478
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,520
including singing and dancing.

479
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:19,440
How can I preserve

480
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,960
Dongzhou's honor?

481
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:22,600
Also,

482
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:23,960
I heard

483
00:20:23,970 --> 00:20:25,440
that Mr. Chu will attend the banquet

484
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,760
as the Director of Astrology.

485
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:29,480
He'll be recording
the meeting of the two states.

486
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:31,240
I don't want him

487
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,720
to see me being overshadowed.

488
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:37,440
I see.

489
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:38,730
So,

490
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,690
it's not the princess
you're nervous about,

491
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:42,390
but Zimo, right?

492
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:46,630
Jiangli, do you have any ideas?

493
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:48,790
Qingqing,

494
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,310
you've traveled through all four states

495
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:52,590
and seen the world's
finest sights and treasures.

496
00:20:53,150 --> 00:20:54,110
I think

497
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,240
you should just show everyone

498
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,550
the most beautiful thing

499
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:57,920
in your eyes.

500
00:20:59,390 --> 00:21:01,240
The most beautiful thing...

501
00:21:02,450 --> 00:21:03,550
Let me think.

502
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,080
Jiangli,

503
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:08,070
I think I know what I'll prepare.

504
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:14,150
- Move the drum to the left.
- Yes.

505
00:21:14,150 --> 00:21:15,250
- Align the sides.
- Sure.

506
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:16,240
Place it here.

507
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:17,290
Let's go check over there.

508
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:18,160
Jiangli.

509
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:20,000
Jiangli,

510
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,200
this is some mare's milk wine

511
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,550
I brought from home for you.

512
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,680
I thought it might be useful
for today's banquet.

513
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:27,400
It'd be a good treat
for our distinguished guests.

514
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,040
By the way, Jiangli,

515
00:21:33,390 --> 00:21:34,630
it's such a grand event.

516
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:36,280
Why is this visit

517
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:37,310
from Xizhou so important?

518
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,310
In the past five years,

519
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:40,630
Dongzhou and Xizhou

520
00:21:40,630 --> 00:21:42,000
have had some minor conflicts,

521
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,790
so the Prefect is giving this visit

522
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:44,680
special attention.

523
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:46,350
The Grand Lady and the princess

524
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,720
are both involved in state affairs.

525
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:49,040
So, we must treat them well

526
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,310
and not make any mistakes.

527
00:21:50,490 --> 00:21:51,350
Alright.

528
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:52,820
I'll stay and help you arrange things.

529
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:54,200
Let's check the stage.

530
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,280
Let's go.

531
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:07,460
(Princess Chuya,
Grand Princess of Xizhou)

532
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:24,940
(Peace and Prosperity)

533
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,720
Grand Lady, you're finally here.

534
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:28,240
After such a long journey,

535
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,790
you still look so energetic.

536
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:31,480
How admirable.

537
00:22:33,170 --> 00:22:34,040
By the way,

538
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:36,150
isn't Princess Chuya coming too?

539
00:22:36,150 --> 00:22:37,960
Where is she?

540
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:40,720
My granddaughter
has always been carefree.

541
00:22:41,070 --> 00:22:43,480
On the way here,
she spotted a wild rabbit,

542
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,520
so she went to chase it.

543
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:56,760
Grandmother.

544
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,390
Did you

545
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:00,390
let the rabbit go?

546
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,960
The rabbit's belly was bulging.

547
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,440
It must be pregnant,

548
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,350
so I let it go.

549
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,550
I've heard of Princess Chuya's

550
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:09,520
impressive reputation,

551
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:10,680
and seeing her today,

552
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:12,440
I can see she lives up to it.

553
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:14,630
Princess Chuya is no ordinary woman.

554
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,830
She excels in horsemanship and tactics.

555
00:23:17,150 --> 00:23:18,350
She's a true heroine.

556
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:21,630
Go and greet Lady Wang and Lady Shu.

557
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:24,760
Greetings, Lady Wang.

558
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:26,630
Greetings, ladies.

559
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,110
Grand Lady, you brought

560
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:32,070
Princess Chuya here
for the Peace Banquet.

561
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:32,920
You must

562
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:35,110
value Dongzhou greatly.

563
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:36,760
Of course.

564
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:39,240
Xizhou and Dongzhou
are closely connected.

565
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:45,550
The young ladies here
are quite charming as well.

566
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,110
You're delicate and graceful.

567
00:23:47,630 --> 00:23:48,470
I like you.

568
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:53,150
Grand Lady, you can rest

569
00:23:53,150 --> 00:23:54,960
with the princess
at the post house for now.

570
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,680
Tonight, at the Peace Banquet,

571
00:23:56,960 --> 00:23:58,790
the young people from both states

572
00:23:58,790 --> 00:24:00,070
can have a good time tonight.

573
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:01,670
Thank you.

574
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:04,670
Let's go.

575
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:06,950
Yulan,

